==歷史==

'''沙樂琴'''的名字源於[[波斯語|波斯語]]，意思是漂亮的聲音或旋律，可能起源於今日[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]的地區，最初被稱為低音 rubab。<ref name=bassrebab>{{cite web| url = http://www.chandrakantha.com/articles/indian_music/sarod.html| title = Sarod| accessdate = 2006-12-02| last = Courtney| first = David| publisher = David and Chandrakantha Courtney| archive-date = 2006-12-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061206021918/http://www.chandrakantha.com/articles/indian_music/sarod.html| dead-url = yes}}</ref> 

